sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Activity Register Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open register URL for activity
    UI->>LW: mount(id)
    LW->>DB: Load activity
    DB-->>LW: Activity record
    LW->>LW: register() auto-run

    LW->>DB: Resolve current student profile
    alt No student profile
        DB-->>LW: Student not found
        LW-->>UI: Error toast
    else Student exists
        LW->>DB: Check existing registration
        alt Already registered
            DB-->>LW: Existing row found
            LW-->>UI: Error toast
        else Not registered
            LW->>DB: Create activity registration
            LW->>DB: Create related calendar events
            DB-->>LW: Saved
            LW-->>UI: Success toast + redirect to details
        end
    end
